headline.main: Oil Has Carried the Sheiks Far Into the 20th Century; Up from Feudalism on the Persian Gulf

docs.abstract: article on wealth of several Middle East states from oil and on progress it has brought; chart showing '73 GNP per capita of Saudi Arabia, Iraq, Kuwait, Iran, Algeria, Libya and United Arab Emirates, all compared with US per capita GNP; drawing
